{"id": 932, "genre": 1001, "title": "你见过哪些“不说人话”？", "description": "请说人话。", "record_count": 4450, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183756Mo3XhFPUfyRw1Cga.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-14T11:05:17Z", "options": [{"id": 67584, "content": "说真的，你别搞得我们之间有什么纠葛似的～丫的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67585, "content": "你一天想这事不累吗～我觉得大家都是同学，你有什么不满足现状的", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67586, "content": "都行", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157963}, {"id": 67587, "content": "你放过她好吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67588, "content": "我问～你还好吗？  她回了句～特别好！那一刻～我都气蒙了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67844, "content": "你最近好吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565486}, {"id": 67589, "content": "别比比了，该干嘛干嘛去", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67590, "content": "你拽着人家不放干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67591, "content": "到你妈的止，自作你妹的情", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67593, "content": "开学就和我主动说了一句话：嗨！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67594, "content": "你说～没想到和你说话这么顺利，你总算没提你哪些奇奇怪怪的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67595, "content": "主要看气质", "image": "img/option/option/201606061616296nK3E4SMjN2OQtJz.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568979}, {"id": 67596, "content": "说真的，你以后说话过过脑子，", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67852, "content": "关心一下别人，他会和你说，你怎么那么闲", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569845}, {"id": 68364, "content": "我是一个有什么就说什么的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572292}, {"id": 67597, "content": "这是最后一次了～听到了没～记住了没～", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568970}, {"id": 67853, "content": "拿着教辅答案的老师：这道题很简单的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565486}, {"id": 67598, "content": "吓死宝宝了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568994}, {"id": 67599, "content": "你是不是讨厌我？\n你要这么想，我也没办法。\n懵逼Orz", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568995}, {"id": 67600, "content": "退学费要找我们财务", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568997}, {"id": 67601, "content": "下面我简单说两句", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566746}, {"id": 67602, "content": "这和我有什么关系？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217366}, {"id": 67603, "content": "某客户每次收到我们的稿子就说：逻辑不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473586}, {"id": 67859, "content": "这个问题没法解决，部门情况不同啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350217}, {"id": 67604, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211900}, {"id": 67605, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211900}, {"id": 68629, "content": "1. 没必要的洋泾浜：“这个问题somehow就是比较critical，that's why我就这样处理。” 2. 没必要的台湾腔：“就si...对啊...zen的！...对啊...(到底什么就对啊？）3. 空洞硬要拿英文塞：\"I dont't know...like...I don't know...\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572959}, {"id": 67606, "content": "关我嗨事", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453302}, {"id": 69142, "content": "给我们销售装上定位。 真是日", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161627xJr09I5EHGPTqfSK.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575418}, {"id": 67607, "content": "这个我要去核实下，核实好了再给你答复", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514967}, {"id": 67608, "content": "现在这么早就说支持董先生，会不会给人一种内定啊钦点的感觉？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453287}, {"id": 67609, "content": "我能说些什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569018}, {"id": 67610, "content": "再说！！！！！！！！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568154}, {"id": 67611, "content": "额/呃/…/。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567787}, {"id": 67612, "content": "我先打断你一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566617}, {"id": 67613, "content": ".", "image": "img/option/option/201606061616057P0wGgflCuO1bU94.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415943}, {"id": 67869, "content": "滚犊子，这里老子说的算", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569914}, {"id": 67614, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569028}, {"id": 67615, "content": "还没有男朋友啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569027}, {"id": 67616, "content": "把相应的东西找出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500721}, {"id": 67617, "content": "科比今天退役了，1996-2016，致我们一起走过的年轻岁月。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161604bQmN4ixcA5BM0CqW.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569025}, {"id": 67873, "content": "质感，你懂吗？我想要图标扁平化有质感！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541998}, {"id": 67618, "content": "有一句话我不知当讲不当讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487179}, {"id": 67619, "content": "anyway ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232647}, {"id": 67620, "content": "你们定！…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340614}, {"id": 67621, "content": "和你有什么关系……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 74460}, {"id": 67622, "content": "你是怎么和他们沟通的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 47660}, {"id": 67623, "content": "我和她真的没有什么，我们就是朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561969}, {"id": 67624, "content": "但是的前面", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 496467}, {"id": 67625, "content": "说、话、", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569032}]}